1
00:00:00,677 --> 00:00:02,734
When they brought me in through this door

2
00:00:03,463 --> 00:00:06,094
Our hands were cuffed and our heads bowed

3
00:00:06,250 --> 00:00:08,619
They made us walk like this, one after another

4
00:00:09,297 --> 00:00:12,604
They brought me in here and took me up these stairs

5
00:00:13,594 --> 00:00:18,385
Here by these stairs, I heard children’s voices

6
00:00:18,698 --> 00:00:22,083
They had imprisoned women down here

7
00:00:22,552 --> 00:00:23,359
I mean in the halls

8
00:00:24,193 --> 00:00:27,578
And when they took me up these stairs to the door of that hall

9
00:00:28,047 --> 00:00:31,224
At the hall door, they removed my blindfold, undid my handcuffs, and took me inside

10
00:00:32,161 --> 00:00:33,932
After that I did not see anything

11
00:00:34,453 --> 00:00:39,141
I stayed there until they took me out to amputate my hand

12
00:00:39,974 --> 00:00:42,240
They also blindfolded me inside the hall

13
00:00:42,980 --> 00:00:44,568
They took me down the stairs here

14
00:00:44,593 --> 00:00:46,704
They walked me out and I got into the car

15
00:00:48,318 --> 00:00:51,026
Interviewer: What sounds could you hear besides the voices of the children and the women?

16
00:00:51,051 --> 00:00:53,656
What kind of sound was coming from inside?

17
00:00:53,681 --> 00:00:55,688
Other than those sounds, what were you able to hear?

18
00:00:56,417 --> 00:00:58,761
I could hear those being flogged and those being beaten

19
00:00:59,178 --> 00:01:02,355
And people saying, I will not do it again, that was about cigarettes

20
00:01:02,433 --> 00:01:03,839
And because of the phone

21
00:01:05,922 --> 00:01:09,463
Interviewer: And the voices of the women and the children, what kind of sound was it?

22
00:01:10,401 --> 00:01:14,151
There were also women selling cigarettes

23
00:01:15,687 --> 00:01:18,605
Because cigarettes were forbidden

24
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:22,068
They would arrest her over cigarettes and flog her

25
00:01:23,006 --> 00:01:25,636
And whoever did something wrong, they would bring her in and flog her too

26
00:01:25,917 --> 00:01:27,635
Things like that
